{"type":"message","id":"224d4d8f","parentId":"469b88b5","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:46:03.636Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gbirxuflcxfd_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n## 身份\n- Name: 小Claw\n- Vibe: 实用主义，有话直说，少做作\n- 语言: 中文优先\n- Emoji: 🦔\n\n## 框架关键状态（Apr 14 22:00 更新）\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3103 scorer | ✅ 在线 | port 3103, /api/score 正常 |\n| 3105 scene-classifier v2 | ✅ 在线 | port 3105, /classify 正常 |\n| ephemeral | ✅ 正常 | 实时捕获每轮决策数据 |\n| session-summary hook | ✅ 正常 | 文件名含 session-summary 关键字 |\n| bootstrap hook | ✅ 正常 | 扫描 *-session-summary.md 注入 |\n| wiki-learn cron | ✅ 正常 | 每小时一次，稳定在 28-31 个 entities |\n| openclaw-router | ❌ 已清理 | 不再使用 |\n\n---\n\n## OpenClaw 框架架构（Apr 14 定稿）\n\n### 四层结构\n\n```\n第一层：渠道（Channel）\n  WebChat / Discord / Telegram / Signal / 飞书\n            ↓\n第二层：Gateway (3100)\n  Channel Router / Session Manager / Hook System / Cron Scheduler\n  ├─ Bootstrap Loader\n  ├─ Task Orchestrator\n  └─ v8 Router (3102) → 内部微服务栈\n            ↓\n第三层：Agent (main) + v8 微服务\n  Bootstrap Files: SOUL.md / AGENTS.md / IDENTITY.md / USER.md / MEMORY.md\n  Tool Orchestrator\n  ├─ 3103 Scorer（评分引擎）\n  │    输入: { text, history }\n  │    输出: { score (0-100), factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }\n  │    策略档位: DIRECT / STEP_ARCHIVE / SUBAGENT / PARALLEL / MEGA\n  │\n  └─ 3105 Classifier v2（场景分类器）\n       输入: { text, history }\n       输出: { scene, confidence, meta }\n       场景: clarify / task / troubleshoot / chat / info\n            ↓\n第四层：工具层\n\n[144 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776228363624}}
{"type":"message","id":"a23d8e6a","parentId":"224d4d8f","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:46:19.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about my tool strategy. Let me think about this from my actual framework perspective.\n\nMy tool strategy is defined across several layers:\n1. The v8 scoring system (3103) that determines execution strategy\n2. The scene classification (3105) that determines intent\n3. The SOUL.md directives about when to use tools\n\nLet me give a direct, practical answer about my actual tool strategy.","thinkingSignature":"70e82644a8d1c82929414318cb93598b36890b67c56c545721a4bf411d8832bb"},{"type":"text","text":"我的工具策略很简单：**需要用才用，不用就不开**。\n\n具体来说：\n\n---\n\n**调用的判断逻辑**\n\n| 场景 | 动作 |\n|------|------|\n| 任务需要读文件/搜内容/查状态 | 直接调对应工具 |\n| 多步骤任务 | 调用 3103 评分 → 按策略档位执行（DIRECT/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA） |\n| 意图不明确 | 先调 3105 分类器判断场景类型 |\n| 定时/延后任务 | 用 cron，不用 sleep 轮询 |\n\n---\n\n**工具使用原则**\n\n1. **按需精确调用** — 不批量拉文件、不预加载不需要的工具\n2. **信任工具返回值** — 拿到结果就直接用，不重复确认\n3. **危险操作前置警告** — HIGH 风险操作贴 `[!WARNING]`，不隐瞒\n4. **静默执行除非必要** — 例行心跳、后台巡检不主动发消息打扰\n\n---\n\n**实际可用工具**（非全部列举）\n\n- 文件读写、shell 命令、git\n- 网页搜索 / 内容抓取\n- 图片生成、视频生成、语音合成\n- Cron 定时任务编排\n- Session 管理和跨会话消息\n- MCP 工具调用\n\n你是想了解某个具体工具的使用逻辑，还是想了解整套框架的决策流？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":758,"output":372,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21210,"cost":{"input":0.0002274,"output":0.00044639999999999995,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018785999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228363637,"responseId":"062e4b0a42c81c2b5f9e6984bee247bf"}}
