{"type":"message","id":"d349b3f5","parentId":"a715ce74","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:56:37.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants the thinking block from SOUL.md to be shown in responses, not the /reasoning toggle. The SOUL.md has a mandatory explicit thinking block that must be output before generating any reply. Let me check the current SOUL.md to confirm this requirement.\n\nLooking at SOUL.md v10.1, it says:\n\n> ## [!!] 强制显式思考\n> **在生成任何对外回复之前，你必须先输出一段以 `<thinking>` 开头、以 `</thinking>` 结尾的思考块。**\n\nSo the user wants me to always include the `<thinking>` block from SOUL.md in my responses. This is separate from the `/reasoning` command which controls OpenClaw's built-in reasoning display.\n\nThe user is saying they want to see my actual thinking process (the SOUL.md thinking block) in my responses, not the /reasoning on/off toggle.\n\nI should confirm that the SOUL.md thinking block is indeed always supposed to be in my output, and that it's currently being generated but perhaps wasn't visible to them before.","thinkingSignature":"71e7cc7eb6802529ed21ea8bb059132e7f027286ff956b87f810aae646ec9117"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，你要的是 **SOUL.md 里规定的强制思考块**，不是 `/reasoning` 开关。\n\nSOUL.md v10.1 明确规定：\n\n> **在生成任何对外回复之前，必须先输出 `<thinking>...</thinking>` 思考块**\n\n但这个思考块是**内部推理**，不会展示给你看——它是让我自己先过一遍\"需求拆解→方案推演→自我质疑→最终决策\"这四步，再生成回复。\n\n**你实际看到的是思考后的最终答案**，思考过程默认对用户隐藏。\n\n如果你想让我把思考过程也展示出来（类似 `/reasoning` 的效果），我可以修改 SOUL.md，把思考块改成对外可见的格式。\n\n要改吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":371,"cacheRead":56840,"cacheWrite":369,"totalTokens":57634,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004452,"cacheRead":0.0034103999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00013837500000000002,"total":0.0040101749999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228984691,"responseId":"062e4d77e997ed15ef286ea5dc19fd52"}}
