{"type":"message","id":"8bf65e38","parentId":"8029d23f","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:35:40.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also check the one that's ranked #1 - `agent-browser-clawdbot` which has a more detailed description from the article.\n\nLet me summarize all the findings:","thinkingSignature":"cbddcf295a1fdaa87451be2b7411abfe3ca120021e5fe115ab123ac2deb5ac46"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了，以下是 5 个 agent-browser 技能的介绍：\n\n---\n\n### 1️⃣ `agent-browser-clawdbot` ⭐ 推荐\n- **评分：** 3.964（最高）\n- **Owner：** matrixy\n- **版本：** 0.1.0\n- **特点：** Headless 浏览器自动化 CLI，针对 AI 代理优化，支持无障碍树快照（accessibility tree snapshots）和基于引用的元素选择\n- **适合：** 需要精确元素定位和辅助功能树分析的复杂网页操作\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ `ws-agent-browser`\n- **评分：** 3.780\n- **Owner：** fhbillwer\n- **版本：** 1.0.0\n- **特点：** 浏览器智能控制，支持自动化操作、截图、填表、数据抓取\n- **适合：** 通用网页自动化任务\n\n---\n\n### 3️⃣ `openclaw-agent-browser`\n- **评分：** 3.722\n- **Owner：** bodietron\n- **版本：** 1.0.0\n- **特点：** Headless 浏览器自动化 CLI，用于导航页面、填写表单、点击按钮、截图、提取数据\n- **适合：** 基础网页交互操作\n\n---\n\n### 4️⃣ `openclaw-agent-browser-clawdbot`\n- **评分：** 3.686\n- 与上面类似，Clawdbot 定制版\n\n---\n\n### 5️⃣ `agent-browser-cli`\n- **评分：** 3.680\n- **Owner：** joshhuang123\n- **版本：** 1.0.0\n- **特点：** 通用浏览器自动化 CLI，支持签到、填表、截图、信息抓取\n- **触发条件：** 用户要求自动化浏览器操作、需要签到/填表/点击按钮、抓取网页内容作为研究素材\n\n---\n\n**推荐安装 `agent-browser-clawdbot`**（评分最高，AI 代理友好）。要装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":380,"output":444,"cacheRead":73408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74232,"cost":{"input":0.00011399999999999999,"output":0.0005327999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00440448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00505128}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776231331196,"responseId":"062e56a2d9e322860f2b518eac55a2af"}}
