hem. I need to reconsider what the user actually asked for. They wanted a deep analysis of the agent-browser options, not just a surface-level comparison. The most critical factors are rating (which reflects real user satisfaction), update frequency (showing active maintenance), and version maturity. `agent-browser-clawdbot` has the highest rating at 3.964 but is version 0.1.0 and hasn't been updated in 28 days, which is concerning. Meanwhile, `agent-browser-cli` was updated today with a v1.0.0 version and has Chinese-language support, making it more actively maintained and accessible for the user.\n\nThe key insight is that `agent-browser-clawdbot` is clearly the most popular choice based on rating, while the newer options show recent development activity. I should present both the quality signal from ratings and the freshness signal from updates, letting the user understand the trade-offs between established popularity and active development.","thinkingSignature":"cd4287003a34ba4140e29150f75440a4232a3311a251bf5f3f770cac914e5f55"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 深度分析\n\n**数据对比：**\n\n| 技能 | 评分 | 版本 | 最后更新 | 维护状态 |\n|------|------|------|----------|----------|\n| `agent-browser-clawdbot` | 3.964 ⭐ | 0.1.0 | 2026-03-18（28天前） | 较老，版本未破1 |\n| `openclaw-agent-browser` | 3.722 | 1.0.0 | 2026-04-15（**今天！**） | 极活跃，v1.0.0稳定版 |\n| `agent-browser-cli` | 3.680 | 1.0.0 | 2026-04-15（**今天！**） | 极活跃，v1.0.0稳定版 |\n| `ws-agent-browser` | 3.780 | 1.0.0 | 2026-03-10（36天前） | 一般活跃 |\n\n---\n\n**关键发现：**\n\n1. **`agent-browser-clawdbot` 评分最高但版本最老**\n   - 3.964 分（用户真实选择的结果）\n   - 版本 0.1.0（说明可能还是 beta）\n   - 28天无更新，可能已被作者放弃\n\n2. **`openclaw-agent-browser` 和 `agent-browser-cli` 今天刚更新**\n   - 都已发布 v1.0.0 稳定版\n   - 说明开发者正在密集维护\n   - 适合长期使用\n\n3. **语言适配**\n   - `agent-browser-cli` 的描述和触发条件是**中文**，更符合你的使用习惯\n   - 其他是英文描述\n\n---\n\n**最终推荐：**\n\n| 场景 | 推荐 |\n|------|------|\n| **追求稳定成熟** | `agent-browser-clawdbot`（久经验证，评分最高） |\n| **追求最新+中文** | `agent-browser-cli`（今天更新，v1.0.0，中文友好） |\n| **追求最新+英文** | `openclaw-agent-browser`（今天更新，v1.0.0，英文） |\n\n考虑到你是中文用户、追求新稳定版，**`agent-browser-cli`** 最匹配。要装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":377,"output":1561,"cacheRead":74240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76178,"cost":{"input":0.0001131,"output":0.0018732,"cacheRead":0.0044544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0064407}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776231424824,"responseId":"062e5700d75c9cd2cbad846564bae4ed"}}
