{"type":"message","id":"bfaaf1b9","parentId":"50acacee","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:40:02.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User is asking if it can \"get information\" - meaning extract data from websites. Based on the SKILL.md I just read, yes it can:\n\n- `agent-browser get text <sel>` - get text\n- `agent-browser get html <sel>` - get HTML\n- `agent-browser get value <sel>` - get input value\n- `agent-browser get title` - get page title\n- `agent-browser get url` - get current URL\n- `agent-browser snapshot` - get accessibility tree\n\nSo yes, it can extract structured data from web pages.","thinkingSignature":"8d24b0ad47ecd494b43650ee75d3dadb86785e4f79dfbaa5210eeee43709b3e9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n能获取。\n\n根据 SKILL.md 的能力：\n\n| 获取内容 | 命令 |\n|----------|------|\n| **文本** | `agent-browser get text <sel>` |\n| **HTML** | `agent-browser get html <sel>` |\n| **输入值** | `agent-browser get value <sel>` |\n| **页面标题** | `agent-browser get title` |\n| **当前URL** | `agent-browser get url` |\n| **完整结构** | `agent-browser snapshot`（可访问性树，包含所有元素ref） |\n\n**典型提取场景：**\n```bash\n# 提取商品价格\nagent-browser get text \".price\"\n\n# 提取表格数据\nagent-browser get html \"table\"\n\n# 提取搜索结果列表\nagent-browser snapshot  # 获取整页结构再逐个提取\n```\n\n比普通爬虫强的是：**能处理动态网页**（JS加载的内容）、**保持登录状态**、**处理弹窗**等。数据提取后还能结构化输出。\n\n要装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":475,"output":332,"cacheRead":76480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77287,"cost":{"input":0.0001425,"output":0.0003984,"cacheRead":0.0045888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005129699999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776231593431,"responseId":"062e57a9adfb654f6adb33b5c2f47f2c"}}
