{"type":"message","id":"a5df72be","parentId":"a18fb903","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:46:21.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Chrome 无法在没有 X server 的 Linux 环境中运行。这是服务器环境，没有图形界面。\n\n有两个选择：\n1. 使用 Playwright 的 headed 模式但配合 Xvfb（虚拟显示）\n2. 或者配置 chromium 使用 --no-sandbox 等参数\n\n让我看看 agent-browser 是否有配置浏览器路径或参数的选项。","thinkingSignature":"640e134505e8af9aafd1c80234e4d1da386eb1d30e5cde4e5b1bab3ce1262e61"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没图形界面，Chrome 无法启动。看看能不能配置无头模式：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7220c674decc481cab1e683a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"agent-browser --help 2>&1 | grep -i \"head\\|display\\|browser\\|chrome\\|arg\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":123,"output":130,"cacheRead":79488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79741,"cost":{"input":0.000036899999999999996,"output":0.000156,"cacheRead":0.00476928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00496218}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776231974689,"responseId":"062e5926e1b13fb4a52ce25ed11017a7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7ecee42","parentId":"a5df72be","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:46:21.380Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7220c674decc481cab1e683a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"agent-browser - fast browser automation CLI for AI agents\nUsage: agent-browser <command> [args] [options]\n  connect <port|url>         Connect to browser via CDP\n  close [--all]              Close browser (--all closes every session)\nGet Info:  agent-browser get <what> [selector]\nCheck State:  agent-browser is <what> <selector>\nFind Elements:  agent-browser find <locator> <value> <action> [text]\nMouse:  agent-browser mouse <action> [args]\nBrowser Settings:  agent-browser set <setting> [value]\n  offline [on|off], headers <json>, credentials <user> <pass>\nNetwork:  agent-browser network <action>\n  trace start|stop [path]    Record Chrome DevTools trace\n  profiler start|stop [path] Record Chrome DevTools profile\n  inspect                    Open Chrome DevTools for the active page\n  batch [--bail] [\"cmd\" ...]  Execute multiple commands sequentially (args or stdin)\n  install                    Install browser binaries\n  profiles                   List available Chrome profiles\n  --profile <name|path>      Chrome profile name (e.g., Default) to reuse login state,\n                             (or AGENT_BROWSER_PROFILE env)\n                             (or AGENT_BROWSER_SESSION_NAME env)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":67,"aggregated":"agent-browser - fast browser automation CLI for AI agents\nUsage: agent-browser <command> [args] [options]\n  connect <port|url>         Connect to browser via CDP\n  close [--all]              Close browser (--all closes every session)\nGet Info:  agent-browser get <what> [selector]\nCheck State:  agent-browser is <what> <selector>\nFind Elements:  agent-browser find <locator> <value> <action> [text]\nMouse:  agent-browser mouse <action> [args]\nBrowser Settings:  agent-browser set <setting> [value]\n  offline [on|off], headers <json>, credentials <user> <pass>\nNetwork:  agent-browser network <action>\n  trace start|stop [path]    Record Chrome DevTools trace\n  profiler start|stop [path] Record Chrome DevTools profile\n  inspect                    Open Chrome DevTools for the active page\n  batch [--bail] [\"cmd\" ...]  Execute multiple commands sequentially (args or stdin)\n  install                    Install browser binaries\n  profiles                   List available Chrome profiles\n  --profile <name|path>      Chrome profile name (e.g., Default) to reuse login state,\n                             (or AGENT_BROWSER_PROFILE env)\n                             (or AGENT_BROWSER_SESSION_NAME env)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776231981370}}
