{"type":"message","id":"e6fc7b64","parentId":"c993b6c3","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found it. In the session `122589c7-91b3-43f3-93c5-2d5af138e58c`, there was a discussion about installing the `openclaw-web-search` plugin and a \"Multi Search Engine\" skill. The user asked about installing the search capability. Let me look more specifically at the session transcript around the Apr 10 area where the user taught me about web search.\n\nActually, looking at the content I found, I can see the user installed the `openclaw-web-search` plugin on April 10. But the user is now asking \"之前不是给你学习了怎么使用搜索的吗？还记得不\" - they're saying they previously taught me how to use web search.\n \nI'm not finding a clear record of them teaching me specifically - the April 10 session shows I installed the plugin and answered questions about pricing, but I don't see an explicit teaching moment about web search usage. Let me check if there's something in the summarize skill that explains how to use web search that the user might be referring to.","thinkingSignature":"a49f4f669d28e743b8377cbd41118e9b14d2ddea28b91e48e498f2278923e65a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ltd5ksgrk0z_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/summarize/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35689,"output":258,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56027,"cost":{"input":0.0107067,"output":0.0003096,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012221099999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776228554423,"responseId":"062e4bc9bc498cb338ed7980a2885cec"}}
