{"type":"message","id":"c0e92ee1","parentId":"44ee6da2","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The weather skill file doesn't exist or has been moved. Let me check the system prompt - it already describes web_search as:\n\n\"web_search - Search the web using DuckDuckGo. Returns titles, URLs, and snippets with no API key required.\"\n\nSo web_search is a built-in tool that uses DuckDuckGo, no API key needed.","thinkingSignature":"d60c3b29d276c8cd3ff98ea6b6fad2f4bd38b067b0d49af2a5c5413c429a11b5"},{"type":"text","text":"`web_search` 是我**内置的搜索工具**，来自 OpenClaw 核心，不依赖任何技能。\n\n**功能：**\n- 用 DuckDuckGo 搜索网页\n- 返回标题、URL、摘要片段\n- **不需要 API key**\n\n**使用方法：**\n```\nweb_search({ query: \"关键词\", count: 5 })\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- 直接可用，配置简单\n- 默认返回 5 条结果\n- 支持 `safeSearch` 参数过滤\n\n---\n\n**对比一下两个搜索方案：**\n\n| | `web_search` | `multi-search-engine` |\n|---|---|---|\n| 来源 | OpenClaw 内置 | 技能插件 |\n| 引擎 | DuckDuckGo | 17个引擎（Google/百度/Bing/…） |\n| API key | ❌ 不需要 | ❌ 不需要 |\n| 配置 | 开箱即用 | 需安装技能 |\n| 适合场景 | 快速简单搜索 | 多引擎/高级运营商 |\n\n---\n\n所以 `web_search` 更轻量，`multi-search-engine` 更强大。你之前教我那个技能主要是为了让我学会用 `web_fetch` 调多引擎搜索的玩法。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35584,"output":313,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55977,"cost":{"input":0.0106752,"output":0.00037559999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012255599999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228654141,"responseId":"062e4c2c9d44d18fae97063ef3cae126"}}
