{"type":"message","id":"ecf312b8","parentId":"9b6a51b9","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me to remember the multi-engine search approach and actually use it. This is a good opportunity to save this to my memory so I remember to use it in the future.","thinkingSignature":"f3db4382ac88f07540c330ec6ee67e770a8c1c455ef3a9e645dc6443a4a473a2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6ztmd005igpf_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.","newText":"## Search - Multi-Engine (Primary)\n\n**When to use:** Search the web for information, news, docs, code examples, etc.\n\n**How:** Use `web_fetch` to call search engine URLs directly — no API key needed.\n\n### Supported Engines\n- Google: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- DuckDuckGo: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}` (privacy, no tracking)\n- Bing: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- Baidu: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- Startpage: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- Brave: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n\n### Advanced Operators\n```\nsite:github.com python    # site-specific search\nfiletype:pdf report       # file type filter\n\"machine learning\"        # exact match\npython -snake             # exclude term\ncat OR dog                # OR logic\n```\n\n### Time Filters (append to URL)\n- `&tbs=qdr:h` — past hour\n- `&tbs=qdr:d` — past day\n- `&tbs=qdr:w` — past week\n- `&tbs=qdr:m` — past month\n\n### DuckDuckGo Bangs (quick redirects)\n```\n!gh tensorflow   → GitHub\n!so react        → Stack Overflow\n!w openclaw      → Wikipedia\n!yt tutorial     → YouTube\n```\n\n### WolframAlpha (calculations & knowledge)\n```\nhttps://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\nhttps://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=integrate+x^2+dx\n```\n\n### Example Usage\n```javascript\nweb_fetch({ url: \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=openclaw+github\" })\nweb_fetch({ url: \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react+hooks\" })\nweb_fetch({ url: \"https://www.google.com/search?q=filetype:pdf+technical+report&tbs=qdr:m\" })\n```\n\n---\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet."}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":710,"cacheRead":55910,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.000852,"cacheRead":0.0033545999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0042066}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776228718739,"responseId":"062e4c6e18b295bb0694c2148274fec7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ea39c21","parentId":"ecf312b8","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.425Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6ztmd005igpf_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 79 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 30 - Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n 31 - Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n 32 ```\n 33 \n+34 ## Search - Multi-Engine (Primary)\n+35 \n+36 **When to use:** Search the web for information, news, docs, code examples, etc.\n+37 \n+38 **How:** Use `web_fetch` to call search engine URLs directly — no API key needed.\n+39 \n+40 ### Supported Engines\n+41 - Google: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n+42 - DuckDuckGo: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}` (privacy, no tracking)\n+43 - Bing: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}`\n+44 - Baidu: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n+45 - Startpage: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n+46 - Brave: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n+47 \n+48 ### Advanced Operators\n+49 ```\n+50 site:github.com python    # site-specific search\n+51 filetype:pdf report       # file type filter\n+52 \"machine learning\"        # exact match\n+53 python -snake             # exclude term\n+54 cat OR dog                # OR logic\n+55 ```\n+56 \n+57 ### Time Filters (append to URL)\n+58 - `&tbs=qdr:h` — past hour\n+59 - `&tbs=qdr:d` — past day\n+60 - `&tbs=qdr:w` — past week\n+61 - `&tbs=qdr:m` — past month\n+62 \n+63 ### DuckDuckGo Bangs (quick redirects)\n+64 ```\n+65 !gh tensorflow   → GitHub\n+66 !so react        → Stack Overflow\n+67 !w openclaw      → Wikipedia\n+68 !yt tutorial     → YouTube\n+69 ```\n+70 \n+71 ### WolframAlpha (calculations & knowledge)\n+72 ```\n+73 https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\n+74 https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=integrate+x^2+dx\n+75 ```\n+76 \n+77 ### Example Usage\n+78 ```javascript\n+79 web_fetch({ url: \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=openclaw+github\" })\n+80 web_fetch({ url: \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react+hooks\" })\n+81 web_fetch({ url: \"https://www.google.com/search?q=filetype:pdf+technical+report&tbs=qdr:m\" })\n+82 ```\n+83 \n+84 ---\n+85 \n 34 ## Why Separate?\n 35 \n 36 Skills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n 37 \n    ...","firstChangedLine":34},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776228735748}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ad03de3","parentId":"2ea39c21","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've added the multi-engine search guide to TOOLS.md so I'll see it and remember to use it.","thinkingSignature":"73699ecd8b3369362ea9d47b4c2164c517d3cdc21f627294da31ff8f012d12ca"},{"type":"text","text":"\n记住了，已写入 `TOOLS.md`。\n\n以后搜索任务会优先用多引擎方案（`web_fetch` 直接调搜索引擎），而不是只依赖内置的 `web_search`。遇到需要多语言搜索、精确筛选、隐私搜索或计算型查询时，会用对应的引擎和运算符。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36578,"output":85,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56743,"cost":{"input":0.0109734,"output":0.000102,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012280199999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776228735758,"responseId":"062e4c7e8aafa680c0bc17ab8f9a0796"}}
