{"type":"message","id":"ff75e5e0","parentId":"022be00e","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_85057ffae95f4957a86469f0","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 735 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2349,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\nagent-browser-cli  Agent Browser CLI\nSummary: 使用 agent-browser CLI 进行浏览器自动化。用于签到、填表、截图、信息抓取等需要控制浏览器的任务。触发条件：(1) 用户要求自动化浏览器操作 (2) 需要签到、填表、点击按钮 (3) 需要抓取网页内容作为研究素材\nOwner: joshhuang123\nCreated: 2026-03-02T00:34:22.105Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-15T04:52:57.503Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nLicense: MIT-0 (Free to use, modify, and redistribute. No attribution required.)\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-03-02T00:34:22.105Z\nChangelog: Vercel agent-browser CLI wrapper for OpenClaw - browser automation for checkins, forms, screenshots\nSecurity: SUSPICIOUS\nWarnings: yes\nChecked: 2026-04-15T04:52:57.324Z\nModel: gpt-5-mini\nFiles:\nSKILL.md  3.7KB  a0e05c23d32a8aa7fe62937868fefe0fae55631f3d68f25c757e63af4c1c81a7  text/markdown","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776231529266}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee3a7bc3","parentId":"ff75e5e0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there's a \"SECURITY: SUSPICIOUS\" warning. Let me inspect the actual SKILL.md content to understand what this skill does and whether the security concern is valid.","thinkingSignature":"de22fa61bc37b0c0b15da9d7cc27c0ba132d0411035058e3d97fbff86249df3d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5256adc1efce4ffd98597da5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect agent-browser-cli --file SKILL.md 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":381,"output":76,"cacheRead":75136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75593,"cost":{"input":0.0001143,"output":0.0000912,"cacheRead":0.00450816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00471366}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776231529281,"responseId":"062e57684b19d593872d6b27fc67e7db"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7a9d4a5","parentId":"ee3a7bc3","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5256adc1efce4ffd98597da5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 2895 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":791,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n---\nname: agent-browser\ndescription: 使用 agent-browser CLI 进行浏览器自动化。用于签到、填表、截图、信息抓取等需要控制浏览器的任务。触发条件：(1) 用户要求自动化浏览器操作 (2) 需要签到、填表、点击按钮 (3) 需要抓取网页内容作为研究素材\n---\n\n# Agent Browser\n\nVercel 出品的浏览器自动化 CLI，基于 Playwright，比标准浏览器工具更快更灵活。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>     # 打开网页\nagent-browser snapshot       # 获取页面可访问性树\nagent-browser click @<ref>   # 点击元素（用ref引用）\nagent-browser fill @<ref> \"内容\"  # 填入内容\nagent-browser close         # 关闭浏览器\n```\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 导航\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>      # 打开URL（别名：goto, navigate）\nagent-browser back            # 后退\nagent-browser forward         # 前进\nagent-browser reload          # 刷新\n```\n\n### 交互\n```bash\nagent-browser click <sel>                    # 点击\nagent-browser dblclick <sel>                  # 双击\nagent-browser fill <sel> \"text\"               # 填入（清空后填）\nagent-browser type <sel> \"text\"               # 输入（追加）\nagent-browser select <sel> <value>             # 选择下拉选项\nagent-browser check <sel>                      # 勾选复选框\nagent-browser uncheck <sel>                   # 取消勾选\nagent-browser press <key>                      # 按键（Enter, Tab, Escape等）\n```\n\n### 获取信息\n```bash\nagent-browser snapshot              # 获取可访问性树（推荐）\nagent-browser get text <sel>        # 获取文本\nagent-browser get html <sel>        # 获取HTML\nagent-browser get value <sel>       # 获取输入值\nagent-browser get title             # 获取页面标题\nagent-browser get url               # 获取当前URL\nagent-browser screenshot [path]     # 截图\nagent-browser screenshot --annotate  # 带标注的截图\n```\n\n### 元素定位\n\n通过 snapshot 输出的 ref（如 @e14）直接引用：\n```bash\nagent-browser click @e14\nagent-browser fill @e13 \"hello\"\n```\n\n或使用 CSS 选择器：\n```bash\nagent-browser click \"#submit\"\nagent-browser fill \"input[name='email']\" \"test@test.com\"\n```\n\n或使用 ARIA 角色查找：\n```bash\nagent-browser find role button click --name \"Submit\"\nagent-browser find text \"Sign In\" click\nagent-browser find label \"Email\" fill \"test@test.com\"\nagent-browser find placeholder \"Search\" type \"query\"\n```\n\n## 典型工作流\n\n### 1. 签到任务\n```bash\n# 打开登录页\nagent-browser open <签到页面URL>\n\n# 获取页面结构\nagent-browser snapshot\n\n# 点击登录/签到按钮（用实际ref替换 @eXX）\nagent-browser click @eXX\n\n# 等待页面加载\nsleep 2\nagent-browser snapshot\n```\n\n### 2. 填表任务\n```bash\nagent-browser open <表单URL>\nagent-browser snapshot\n\n# 填入各字段\nagent-browser find label \"用户名\" fill \"myuser\"\nagent-browser find label \"密码\" fill \"mypassword\"\nagent-browser find role button click --name \"提交\"\n```\n\n### 3. 定时签到（配合cron）\n创建脚本 `~/.openclaw/scripts/daily-checkin.sh`：\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\nagent-browser open <签到URL>\nsleep 2\nagent-browser find role button click --name \"签到\"\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/checkin_$(date +%Y%m%d).png\nagent-browser close\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. **先 snapshot 再操作** - 每次页面变化后重新获取 ref\n2. **添加等待** - 页面加载需要时间，用 `sleep 2` 或等待\n3. **保持浏览器开启** - 多个操作可以在同一浏览器会话中完成\n4. **完成后关闭** - 用 `agent-browser close` 释放资源\n\n## 依赖安装\n\n如果 agent-browser 未安装：\n```bash\nnpm install -g agent-browser\nagent-browser install\n```","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776231534659}}
{"type":"message","id":"741d9ee9","parentId":"d7a9d4a5","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:48:36.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great, now I have the full SKILL.md for agent-browser-cli. Let me provide a comprehensive introduction.","thinkingSignature":"2b4b4d57447d5c9f04e25a4c35d1ca5aaa69b62cddc2da9087ef960a4aeb24fb"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**`agent-browser-cli` 详细介绍**\n\n---\n\n### 一句话定位\nVercel 出品的浏览器自动化 CLI，基于 Playwright，比标准浏览器工具更快更灵活。\n\n---\n\n### 核心能力\n\n| 能力 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **网页导航** | 打开URL、后退、前进、刷新 |\n| **元素交互** | 点击、双击、填写表单、输入文字、下拉选择、勾选复选框、按键 |\n| **信息提取** | 获取文本/HTML/值、页面标题、当前URL |\n| **截图** | 普通截图、带标注截图 |\n| **元素定位** | CSS选择器、ARIA角色查找、ref引用 |\n\n---\n\n### 典型工作流\n\n**签到任务：**\n```bash\nagent-browser open <签到URL>\nagent-browser snapshot          # 获取页面结构和ref\nagent-browser click @eXX        # 用ref点击按钮\n```\n\n**填表任务：**\n```bash\nagent-browser open <表单URL>\nagent-browser find label \"用户名\" fill \"myuser\"\nagent-browser find label \"密码\" fill \"mypassword\"\nagent-browser find role button click --name \"提交\"\n```\n\n**定时自动化（配合cron）：**\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\nagent-browser open <URL>\nagent-browser find role button click --name \"签到\"\nagent-browser screenshot /tmp/checkin_$(date +%Y%m%d).png\nagent-browser close\n```\n\n---\n\n### 安装方式\n```bash\nnpm install -g agent-browser\nagent-browser install\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 注意\n- Security 标记：**SUSPICIOUS**（有警告）\n- 需要先 `snapshot` 获取 ref 再操作\n- 页面加载需要等待时间（用 `sleep`）\n- 完成后要 `close` 释放资源\n\n---\n\n**总结：** 这个工具可以让我真正控制浏览器完成自动化任务（签到/填表/点击），而不是只能抓取静态页面。要安装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1028,"output":433,"cacheRead":75456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76917,"cost":{"input":0.00030839999999999996,"output":0.0005195999999999999,"cacheRead":0.004527359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005355359999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776231534672,"responseId":"062e576ebc441256cadddb391b7cbfce"}}
