{"type":"message","id":"c6c8aaa6","parentId":"6846bd51","timestamp":"2026-04-15T05:51:44.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works! Python Playwright with headless mode works perfectly. So I can use Python Playwright directly instead of agent-browser (which is having issues).\n\nThis is actually better - I can now do browser automation using Python Playwright. Let me update the user that we can use browser automation via Python Playwright instead of the Node.js agent-browser.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了！用 **Python Playwright** 成功跑起来了：\n\n- ✅ 无头模式（headless）\n- ✅ 打开网页成功\n- ✅ 获取标题：Example Domain\n- ✅ 获取内容：528 字符\n\n**结论：** Node.js 版的 `agent-browser` 在这环境有问题，但 **Python Playwright 可以用**。\n\n以后浏览器自动化任务我可以直接用 Python Playwright 实现，功能是一样的：\n- 打开网页、点击、填表\n- 截图\n- 提取数据\n\n要测试一个具体任务吗？比如打开某个网页、截图或者提取内容？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":42560,"output":194,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776232302641,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c04e855b-031b-4a73-b11c-d03cda9c8eed"}}
