{"type":"message","id":"03abc858","parentId":"4629faf0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:13:55.221Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-15 13:51:27 GMT+8] Exec completed (fast-tra, code 0) :: r_playwright/driver/package/lib/vite/traceViewer/playwright-logo.svg /home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/rebrowser_playwright/driver/package/lib/remote/playwrightServer.js…\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-15 14:13 GMT+8] 打开小红书"}],"timestamp":1776233635207}}
{"type":"message","id":"097c4573","parentId":"03abc858","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:14:18.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想打开小红书（xiaohongshu.com）。我可以用 Python Playwright 来做。\n\n这是一个简单的测试任务，让我用浏览器打开小红书。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d8fc670440847238471759b1e90b4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True, args=['--no-sandbox', '--disable-setuid-sandbox'])\n    page = browser.new_page(viewport={'width': 1280, 'height': 720})\n    page.goto('https://www.xiaohongshu.com')\n    page.wait_for_timeout(3000)  # 等待页面加载\n    \n    # 截图\n    page.screenshot(path='/tmp/xiaohongshu.png')\n    \n    title = page.title()\n    url = page.url\n    \n    # 获取页面内容片段\n    content_preview = page.content()[:2000]\n    \n    browser.close()\n    print(f\"Title: {title}\")\n    print(f\"URL: {url}\")\n    print(\"Screenshot saved to /tmp/xiaohongshu.png\")\n    print(f\"Content preview length: {len(content_preview)}\")\nEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":42600,"output":270,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776233635235,"responseId":"019d8fc6455c4ec6843427bee76cbd04"}}
