{"type":"message","id":"04068661","parentId":"1396a6ad","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:18:46.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so:\n- WSL internal IP: 172.23.111.196\n- External IP: 39.184.93.220\n\n这说明 WSL 通过 Windows 的网络连接出去。可能 Windows 有什么网络配置？或者这个 IP 就是用户说的他本地网络的 IP？\n\n等等，用户说\"你跟我用的 IP 不一样\"，意思是用户觉得我的 IP 应该是他的 IP。让我让用户查一下他自己的 IP 是多少。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d8fcab702010d1c6592ecba39a3c3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 5 https://ipinfo.io 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1845,"output":134,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776233914690,"responseId":"019d8fca923e23733c4de0c26752207e"}}
