{"type":"message","id":"845c03a0","parentId":"c623d426","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:18:57.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所以当前环境的 IP 是 39.184.93.220（上海移动）。用户可能用的是不同的网络？\n\n让我问用户他的 IP 是多少，看看是否一样。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n奇怪，我这边查出来也是 **39.184.93.220**（上海移动）。\n\n你在 Windows 上查一下你的 IP 是多少？\n\n查一下：https://ipinfo.io\n\n或者CMD里输：\n```\ncurl https://api.ipify.org\n```\n\n看看是不是同一个。如果一样，那小红书就是单纯对这个 IP 段风控比较严。如果不一样，说明网络走的有差异。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":44586,"output":115,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776233927283,"responseId":"019d8fca2c3a0b47cc6fc91ed0d74865"}}
