{"type":"message","id":"189e4692","parentId":"f94cd9b5","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:20:18.569Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The IP is definitely showing as 39.184.93.220 across multiple services. But the user says they're in Zhejiang. There's a mismatch here.\n\nLet me just tell the user the situation and suggest they check their Windows-side IP and see what's going on. Maybe there's some VPN or network proxy configured on their machine that's routing traffic differently for WSL.\n\nAlso, I should acknowledge that something is odd here - either the user doesn't realize there's a VPN/proxy running, or there's a network configuration issue.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我这显示的 IP 确实很奇怪，查哪个源都是 **39.184.93.220**。\n\n你在 Windows CMD 里查一下你的实际 IP：\n\n```cmd\ncurl https://api.ipify.org\n```\n\n如果你的 IP 是浙江的，而 WSL 里查到的是上海，那说明：\n1. **WSL 网络走了代理/VPN** — Windows 上是不是开着代理？\n2. **移动网络出口在上海** — 39.184.93.220 是移动的 IP，归属地可能显示上海但实际人在浙江\n\n你先查一下两边 IP 是否一致？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":44768,"output":223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776234014790,"responseId":"chatcmpl-384a65b4-9695-41a2-bd7e-72e623b09ca0"}}
