{"type":"message","id":"dfca08b1","parentId":"cadaea54","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:23:19.759Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-15 14:23 GMT+8] C:\\Users\\ll>curl -x http://127.0.0.1:7890 https://api.ipify.org\ncurl: (7) Failed to connect to api.ipify.org port 443 via 127.0.0.1 after 2029 ms: Could not connect to server\n\nC:\\Users\\ll>netsh winhttp show proxy\n\n当前的 WinHTTP 代理服务器设置:\n\n 直接访问(没有代理服务器)。\n\n\nC:\\Users\\ll>curl https://myip.ipip.net\n当前 IP：39.184.93.220 来自于：中国 浙江 台州 移动\n\nC:\\Users\\ll>"}],"timestamp":1776234199750}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c4d33c8","parentId":"dfca08b1","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:23:27.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The user is in Zhejiang (台州), but their IP shows as 39.184.93.220 which is registered to Shanghai but actually being used in Zhejiang. This is normal for mobile networks - the IP allocation doesn't always match the physical location.\n\nSo the issue is NOT that I'm on a remote server - I'm running locally in WSL as the user said. The issue is simply that Xiaohongshu (小红书) is blocking this IP for some reason - it could be:\n1. Mobile IP range that's flagged as suspicious\n2. The IP was previously used for automated access and got flagged\n3. Xiaohongshu's risk control is triggered\n\nSo I should clarify to the user that we're both on the same IP (39.184.93.220), but Xiaohongshu is blocking that specific IP. The issue isn't about being on a remote server - it's about the IP itself being blocked or flagged by Xiaohongshu.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了！你的 IP 就是 **39.184.93.220**（浙江台州 移动），跟我这边一样。\n\n所以不是远程服务器的问题 — **我们用的是同一个 IP**。\n\n问题是：**小红书单独把这个 IP 封了或者风控了**。\n\n可能原因：\n1. 移动这个 IP 段被标记为\"数据中心/非住宅\"\n2. 这个 IP 之前可能被大量访问/爬取过\n3. 小红书风控比较严\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. **等一段时间** — 可能临时封禁，过会自动解\n2. **换 WiFi** — 如果用手机热点或别的网络，IP 就换了\n3. **你本地登录** — 你自己打开小红书，截图发我\n\n你先试下手机热点换个 IP能不能打开？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":44822,"output":369,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776234199777,"responseId":"chatcmpl-af0c2989-a067-4452-a9a8-a66030c4eb88"}}
