{"type":"message","id":"df3fd6b8","parentId":"fc4a908e","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:24:36.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user tested curl with the proxy (7890 port) to xiaohongshu.com and it failed to connect. This means either:\n1. The proxy on port 7890 is not actually running (the user might have turned it off)\n2. The proxy isn't working properly\n3. The proxy can't connect to xiaohongshu.com either\n\nWait, the user said earlier that `curl -x http://127.0.0.1:7890 https://api.ipify.org` also failed with \"Failed to connect\". And they showed `netstat` didn't show anything listening on 7890.\n\nSo the proxy on 7890 is NOT actually running. The user needs to start their proxy software first.\n\nBut wait, let me re-read... The user didn't test with a working proxy. They're trying to use port 7890 but that's not running.\n\nThe key question is: do they have a working proxy? If yes, what's the port? If no, they need to start one.\n\nLet me ask them to confirm if the proxy is actually running.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n7890 端口根本没监听，说明你**代理软件没开**。\n\n之前的 `netstat -ano | findstr :7890` 应该也没结果吧？\n\n你先去打开代理软件（Clash、V2Ray 之类的），确保端口有在监听，然后再测。\n\n或者你现在有能用的代理吗？告诉我端口是多少，我来改 OpenClaw 的配置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":46041,"output":300,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776234270431,"responseId":"chatcmpl-40f88ebd-6c24-4a10-bdd5-18c859dc3ba9"}}
