{"type":"message","id":"cfa73fd7","parentId":"da3aed72","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:25:37.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says they don't have a proxy. So they can't use a proxy to access Xiaohongshu.\n\nThe core issue is: the mobile IP (39.184.93.220) is being blocked by Xiaohongshu. Without a proxy, there's no way to change the IP.\n\nOptions:\n1. Wait and try again later (maybe the temporary block will be lifted)\n2. Use mobile hotspot to get a different IP\n3. User accesses Xiaohongshu locally and sends screenshots to me\n\nSince the user doesn't have a proxy, the only practical solutions are:\n1. Try using mobile hotspot (different IP)\n2. User manually accesses and shares screenshots\n3. Give up on Xiaohongshu for now\n\nLet me explain this simply.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没有代理的话，这个移动 IP 就过不去。\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n1. **手机热点** — 换个 IP（电信/联通）\n2. **你本地打开** — 截图发我，我来分析内容\n3. **放弃小红书** — 换个网站先玩\n\n你想怎么搞？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":46164,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776234313735,"responseId":"019d8fd09fb438b33451c8b86cd3697a"}}
