{"type":"message","id":"131ead49","parentId":"fab76818","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:28:19.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying connecting to mobile hotspot would be too slow (卡死了). That makes sense - mobile data might be slower and they don't want to switch.\n\nLet me think of alternatives:\n1. Use the user's local browser - they can browse and send me screenshots\n2. Find a website that works with the current IP\n3. Just accept the limitation\n\nActually, the simplest solution is: the user can just browse on their local machine and send me screenshots/内容, and I can help analyze. That's what we'd normally do anyway since I can't see the browser anyway.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n也对，手机热点太慢。\n\n那就这样吧：\n- **你来操作** — 电脑开小红书/贴吧\n- **截图发我** — 我帮你分析内容\n\n反正我本来就看不见浏览器界面，只能看你发的图。😂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":46821,"output":167,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776234496406,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7ce0b84f-4ec9-4415-9dbf-bbc71a7268dd"}}
