{"type":"message","id":"e4c0f1ad","parentId":"100e272f","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:35:55.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个很好的问题！用户说直接在Windows浏览器里可以访问小红书和贴吧，但我用WSL里的Python Playwright访问却被拦截。\n\n这说明问题不是IP本身（因为用的是同一个IP），而是：\n\n1. **User-Agent** - Windows浏览器和Playwright headless的User-Agent不一样\n2. **Cookie/Session** - Windows浏览器可能有登录状态的cookie\n3. **指纹检测** - 小红书/贴吧可能检测到是自动化脚本（headless模式有特征）\n4. **Referer** - 没有正常的Referer\n5. **TLS指纹** - Playwright的TLS指纹可能被识别\n\n让我解释这个，并建议用更隐蔽的方式试试。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好问题！不是 IP 的问题，是**浏览器特征**的问题：\n\n| 对比 | Windows 浏览器 | WSL Playwright |\n|------|----------------|----------------|\n| IP | 一样 ✅ | 一样 ✅ |\n| User-Agent | `Chrome/Win` | `HeadlessChrome` |\n| Cookie | 登录状态 | 无 |\n| Referer | 正常 | 空 |\n| Canvas/WebGL | 正常 | 可能被识别 |\n\n小红书/贴吧检测到你是**自动化脚本（headless）**，不是真实浏览器。\n\n**试试加上 Cookie 和正常 User-Agent：**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8a856c9372224f49be1c83f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(\n        headless=True, \n        args=[\n            '--no-sandbox', \n            '--disable-setuid-sandbox',\n            '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'  # 隐藏自动化特征\n        ]\n    )\n    context = browser.new_context(\n        user_agent='Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/124.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n        viewport={'width': 1920, 'height': 1080}\n    )\n    page = context.new_page()\n    \n    # 去掉 webdriver 属性\n    page.add_init_script(\"\"\"\n        Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', {get: () => undefined});\n    \"\"\")\n    \n    page.goto('https://tieba.baidu.com', timeout=15000)\n    page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n    \n    page.screenshot(path='/tmp/tieba2.png')\n    title = page.title()\n    url = page.url\n    \n    context.close()\n    browser.close()\n    print(f\"Title: {title}\")\n    print(f\"URL: {url}\")\nEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":47270,"output":571,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776234946235,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4389a7e3-2324-47c4-be41-f52bc819be8b"}}
