{"type":"message","id":"74ca14ea","parentId":"fd0e6eb8","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:51:44.131Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"百度也要验证码。和之前一样的问题 - 这个 IP 被百度风控了。\n\n这和直接访问 Tieba/百度是一样的结果 - 验证码墙。\n\n搜索百度相关的东西都会触发验证码。\n\nLet me just tell the user the situation - the IP is being blocked by Baidu's security check, so we can't search Baidu or access Tieba directly.","thinkingSignature":"c96cc6ce1aa87d1523aad8873257ecd508335c9ca0dd0569db97b91137beaf6c"},{"type":"text","text":"百度也弹验证码了 — 跟之前访问贴吧/小红书一样，这个 IP 被国内网站集体风控。\n\n**多引擎搜索能用的前提是：搜索引擎本身能访问**。但现在这个 IP 对百度/Bing/Google 都触发了验证。\n\n**结论：这 IP 处于\"高风险\"状态，任何搜索都难。**\n\n你本地浏览器能搜是因为你那边 IP 不一样。你要真想让我搜索，得：\n1. 手机开热点让我走那个 IP\n2. 或者把搜索内容发我，我来查"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39765,"output":185,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60030,"cost":{"input":0.011929499999999999,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013356299999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776235896112,"responseId":"062e6877e20a27323e4240f0ae587f93"}}
