{"type":"message","id":"afad310d","parentId":"a5cf0504","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:55:15.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to \"study\" this information about using Microsoft Edge for browser automation with OpenClaw. They've provided detailed instructions about two approaches:\n\n1. **Managed browser (OpenClaw-managed)** - using a separate, isolated Edge instance\n2. **Attach to existing session** - connecting to an already-running Edge browser with remote debugging\n\nThis is using Edge's Chromium base to do browser automation. Let me understand this and summarize it.\n\nKey points:\n- OpenClaw's browser automation is based on Chromium, so it naturally supports Edge\n- New versions have simplified the process, no need for extra browser extensions\n- Two methods:\n  1. **Managed browser** - separate isolated Edge instance with its own cache/settings, configured via `openclaw.json` with `browser.enabled: true`, `defaultProfile: \"openclaw\"`, and `executablePath` pointing to Edge\n  2. **Attach to existing session** - connect to a running Edge browser via remote debugging port 9222, which can reuse existing login state\n\nThis is useful information for the user since their IP is blocked from certain sites, but if they connect to their local Edge which has existing login cookies, the automation might work better.","thinkingSignature":"7c7f650cb57c28e6f959cd9f7608f8cf76532dcb8f1ef67a34496d06116008a4"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，已学习。\n\n**核心结论：用 Edge 代替 chromium-browser**\n\nOpenClaw 浏览器自动化基于 Chromium，天然支持 Edge。有两种方式：\n\n| 方案 | 适用场景 | 优点 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **方案一：托管模式** | 日常自动化任务 | 隔离沙盒，干净不干扰日常浏览器 |\n| **方案二：连接现有会话** | 操作已登录网站（贴吧/小红书） | 直接复用登录态，跳过风控 |\n\n**关键配置（方案一）：**\n```json\n{\n  \"browser\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"defaultProfile\": \"openclaw\",\n    \"executablePath\": \"C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\Microsoft\\\\Edge\\\\Application\\\\msedge.exe\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**关键配置（方案二）：**\n1. 先以调试模式启动 Edge：`msedge.exe --remote-debugging-port=9222 --user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"`\n2. 告诉 OpenClaw 连接到本地 Edge\n\n---\n\n你想用哪个方案？方案二对我们当前情况更有用 — 直接\"借用\"你已登录的贴吧/小红书会话，省去重新登录和风控问题。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":507,"cacheRead":60438,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60999,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0006083999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0036262799999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004250879999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776236093119,"responseId":"062e693d29b7d1716f96e8a479d09825"}}
