{"type":"message","id":"9cb44900","parentId":"9ee4a079","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:57:57.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The port is not open. I need to ask the user to start Edge with the debugging port. Let me guide them.","thinkingSignature":"4138f8cc1ef26bb052e735249fcc82a00d02bbe79190f9580ba241a6dbbf6cdd"},{"type":"text","text":"端口没开。现在需要你在 **Windows CMD** 里运行这条命令：\n\n```\nmsedge.exe --remote-debugging-port=9222 --user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"\n```\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 先**关掉所有 Edge 窗口**（必须完全退出）\n2. Win + R → 输入 `cmd` → 回车\n3. 粘贴上面的命令 → 回车\n\nEdge 会启动（一个小窗口，和正常浏览器一样）\n\n启动后告诉我，我来连接。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41297,"output":131,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61508,"cost":{"input":0.0123891,"output":0.0001572,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013751099999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776236271868,"responseId":"062e69ef7dae0574ade50eb424122fc0"}}
