{"type":"message","id":"73d58fef","parentId":"94b840c2","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:58:58.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good point! The user is asking: if they close Edge, how can they send me messages? They use the webchat interface in their browser to talk to me. If they close Edge, they lose their browser session.\n\nThe answer is: they shouldn't close their main browser (the one they're using to chat with me). They should:\n1. Keep their chat browser open\n2. Start a NEW Edge window with the debug command (this creates a separate Edge instance with a separate user data directory)\n\nThe `--user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"` creates a temporary, separate user data directory. This means this new Edge instance is completely separate from their normal Edge browser where they're chatting with me.\n\nSo they can have two Edge windows open:\n- Their normal Edge (where they're chatting with me) - keep this open\n- A new debug Edge window (with the command) - this is what we'll use for automation\n\nLet me clarify this.","thinkingSignature":"fa4e2973016f041935cadf10cb48c3485e7a5d135b42fe48d6b2ea2069a0f0fa"},{"type":"text","text":"哈，不用关**你聊天用的**那个 Edge！\n\n命令里的 `--user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"` 会创建一个**独立的临时配置目录**，所以：\n\n- **你正常的 Edge**（现在开着这个网页跟我聊天的）→ 不受影响\n- **新开的调试 Edge**（运行命令后弹出的窗口）→ 单独实例，专门给我们用\n\n**你只需要：**\n1. 正常 Edge 不用动，继续跟我聊天\n2. 新开一个 CMD 窗口运行那个命令\n3. 会弹出一个**新的** Edge 窗口（看起来和正常一样，但数据隔离）\n4. 在那个新窗口里登录贴吧/小红书\n5. 告诉我，我来连接\n\n两个 Edge 可以同时跑，互不干扰。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":352,"cacheRead":61368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.00042239999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0036820799999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00410448}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776236324855,"responseId":"062e6a2329c87a9f11cbbc09325e4096"}}
