{"type":"message","id":"1d1ecf1c","parentId":"d100eea2","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:00:31.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user ran the command but got \"'msedge.exe' is not recognized as an internal or external command\". This means the Edge executable is not in the system PATH. They need to use the full path to msedge.exe.\n\nOn Windows, Edge is usually installed at:\n`C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\\msedge.exe`\nor\n`C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\\msedge.exe`\n\nLet me give them the full path command.","thinkingSignature":"93054e3223eaa3260322f9438c8224ef1bc23401ecef69018d4f03615c04b316"},{"type":"text","text":"Edge 不在 PATH 里，用完整路径。在 CMD 里运行：\n\n```\n\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\\msedge.exe\" --remote-debugging-port=9222 --user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"\n```\n\n如果提示找不到，试这个：\n\n```\n\"C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft\\Edge\\Application\\msedge.exe\" --remote-debugging-port=9222 --user-data-dir=\"%TEMP%\\edge-debug-profile\"\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":199,"cacheRead":61459,"cacheWrite":124,"totalTokens":61836,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00023879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0036875399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0000465,"total":0.003989039999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776236417331,"responseId":"062e6a830a1198df7752b7f99592fd93"}}
