{"type":"message","id":"248d76d0","parentId":"0bd021e9","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:05:26.887Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-15 15:05 GMT+8] C:\\Windows\\System32>netsh interface portproxy show all\n\n侦听 ipv4: 连接到 ipv4:\n\n地址 端口 地址 端口\n--------------- ---------- --------------- ----------\n0.0.0.0 19222 127.0.0.1 9222\n\n\nC:\\Windows\\System32>"}],"timestamp":1776236726878}}
{"type":"message","id":"982eae26","parentId":"248d76d0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:05:41.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The portproxy is set up correctly. The issue might be the Windows Firewall blocking incoming connections to port 19222. Let me check if we can reach it by a different approach.\n\nActually, wait - WSL is on the same machine, so it's going through the Windows network interface. But since we can't connect, let me try a different approach.\n\nLet me check if the issue is the Windows Defender Firewall blocking the port. Alternatively, we could try running the Edge command with `--remote-debugging-port=0.0.0.0:9222` to make it listen on all interfaces, but that might not be supported.\n\nActually, let me try a simpler test - can I ping the Windows host from WSL and get a response? Yes, the ping worked. So the network connectivity is fine.\n\nThe issue is likely the Windows Firewall blocking incoming connections on port 19222. Let me ask the user to try disabling the firewall temporarily or adding an exception.\n\nOr wait - actually, portproxy should work without firewall changes for outbound connections... but wait, the connection is coming FROM WSL to Windows, which is an incoming connection to Windows. So the Windows Firewall might be blocking it.\n\nLet me ask the user to try adding a firewall rule or disable the firewall temporarily for testing.","thinkingSignature":"4a1dc32db3a746c2adb037680e6dc5b77b7cf9aafc83b8d76bf8624464df9e8b"},{"type":"text","text":"portproxy 配置正确。问题应该是防火墙拦了。\n\n试试在**管理员权限的 CMD** 添加防火墙例外：\n\n```\nnetsh advfirewall firewall add rule name=\"OpenClaw Edge Debug\" dir=in action=allow protocol=tcp localport=19222\n```\n\n或者快速测试，先关掉防火墙：\n\n```\nnetsh advfirewall set allprofiles state off\n```\n\n测试完再开回去：\n\n```\nnetsh advfirewall set allprofiles state on\n```\n\n你先试试添加例外规则那条。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":368,"cacheRead":62790,"cacheWrite":13,"totalTokens":63225,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004416,"cacheRead":0.0037673999999999997,"cacheWrite":0.000004875,"total":0.004230075}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776236726908,"responseId":"062e6bb76afc10f19a741aff0d2a5344"}}
