{"type":"message","id":"d0cde4e9","parentId":"95c5ebe0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:06:45.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Connected! I can see Edge/Edg 147.0.3912.60 is running. Now let me connect using Playwright to the existing Edge browser via CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol).\n\nThe webSocketDebuggerUrl is: ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3\n\nNow I can use Playwright to connect to this browser and操作已登录的网站！","thinkingSignature":"b0ca88f3d39b7e982354c168349c23892d49b86fe006c1d4f4205a43f8c38f81"},{"type":"text","text":"连上了！Edge 147 版本，CDP 正常。现在用 Playwright 连接：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ubjtjkwatrvr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport json\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    # 连接到已存在的 Edge 浏览器（通过 CDP）\n    browser = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp(\n        \"ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3\"\n    )\n    \n    # 获取所有上下文（浏览器页面）\n    contexts = browser.contexts\n    print(f\"Browser contexts: {len(contexts)}\")\n    \n    for ctx in contexts:\n        pages = ctx.pages\n        print(f\"  Context with {len(pages)} pages\")\n        for page in pages:\n            print(f\"    Page: {page.title} - {page.url}\")\n    \n    browser.close()\n    print(\"SUCCESS - Connected to Edge!\")\nEOF","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43257,"output":344,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63681,"cost":{"input":0.0129771,"output":0.0004128,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014594699999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776236793118,"responseId":"062e6bf862ec2ae2b5b663479ad6e0e1"}}
