{"type":"message","id":"f4c2909d","parentId":"64dee455","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:14:21.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the logged-in Tieba homepage. The user is \"明天见\"，and it shows their tieba profile with:- 个性域名: tb.1.fb843a56.BUo9zAYTr- 贴吧年龄: 11年11个月- 发帖数量: 3025\n- 精品贴: 7\n- 吧龄: 11.9年\n- 关注: 5\n- 粉丝: 94\n\nThis confirms the CDP connection is working and we have the logged-in state. Now the user can browse and I can take screenshots and interact with Tieba!","thinkingSignature":"16c682ddd74e59f1eca6e57a40f143e992038a8281529c8e1288e43b34b2b4a9"},{"type":"text","text":"登录状态确认！用你的账号了。\n\n**账号信息：**\n- 用户名：明天见\n- 吧龄：11年11个月\n- 发帖：3025\n- 粉丝：94\n\nCDP 连接完全正常！现在可以操作了。\n\n**能做的事：**\n- 浏览帖子、截图\n- 搜索贴吧内容\n- 查看吧内动态\n\n你想看哪个吧？告诉我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47514,"output":216,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67810,"cost":{"input":0.0142542,"output":0.0002592,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015718199999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776237249726,"responseId":"062e6dc16bc8a6fdec1b431f123fc9ab"}}
