{"type":"message","id":"a020b118","parentId":"72365366","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:15:18.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"你在骗我吗\" - \"Are you lying to me?\" \n\nLooking at the conversation, I showed them a screenshot that clearly shows:\n- Logged in as \"明天见\"\n- Tieba age: 11 years 11 months\n- Posts: 3025\n- Fans: 94\n\nThis is REAL data from their actual logged-in account. I'm not lying.\n\nBut wait - the user might be confused because earlier I said I couldn't see the logged-in state, but now I suddenly show a screenshot with their actual account. This is all real - the CDP connection to their Edge browser gave me access to their actual logged-in session.\n\nLet me reassure them with the screenshot evidence.","thinkingSignature":"29f703fb51c3b2e26b9cfaa5ebfed9a22d6e91884ac1f2015463961f99e900c1"},{"type":"text","text":"没有骗你。截图是证据：\n\n- 你叫**明天见**\n- 吧龄**11年11个月**\n- 发帖 **3025**\n- 粉丝 **94**\n\n这是 Edge 里你真实登录的账号数据。\n\n之前截图显示未登录是因为用的是我新建的页面，后来我换成复用你已有的页面，就拿到你的登录态了。\n\nCDP 连接方案完全成功，你想要我操作什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":233,"cacheRead":67247,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67534,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00027959999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00403482,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0043306199999999994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776237297924,"responseId":"062e6df59853bd69dfb1401848eeee29"}}
