{"type":"message","id":"e46685fd","parentId":"139466dd","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:50:08.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to do batch search and analysis on the Rimworld (环世界) tieba forum. Let me retrieve multiple posts and analyze them.\n\nI need to:\n1. Get a list of posts from the forum\n2. For each post, get its content and replies\n3. Analyze and summarize the data\n4. Output the results\n\nLet me start by getting the post list and then fetching a few of the latest posts.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，批量检索环世界吧，分析热门帖子。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d901d370f9dc5747cd87059290de3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 35 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport json\n\nresults = []\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    pg = b.contexts[0].pages[-1]\n    \n    # 获取首页帖子列表\n    pg.goto('https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=环世界', wait_until='domcontentloaded', timeout=15000)\n    pg.wait_for_timeout(5000)\n    \n    # 滚动加载\n    pg.evaluate('window.scrollTo(0, document.body.scrollHeight)')\n    pg.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n    \n    # 获取帖子链接\n    links = pg.query_selector_all('.threadlist_lz a.j_threadlist_threads_link')\n    print(f\"Found {len(links)} threads\")\n    \n    post_data = []\n    for i, link in enumerate(links[:15]):\n        try:\n            href = link.get_attribute('href')\n            title = link.inner_text()\n            if href and title:\n                post_data.append({'title': title[:80], 'href': href})\n                print(f\"{i+1}. {title[:60]}\")\n        except:\n            pass\n    \n    # 获取每个帖子的详细信息\n    print(\"\\n=== 获取帖子详情 ===\")\n    for i, post in enumerate(post_data[:10]):\n        try:\n            full_url = \"https://tieba.baidu.com\" + post['href']\n            pg.goto(full_url, wait_until='domcontentloaded', timeout=10000)\n            pg.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n            \n            # 获取回复数和阅读数\n            reply_count = 0\n            read_count = 0\n            \n            # 尝试获取回复数\n            try:\n                reply_elem = pg.query_selector('.l_posts_num .replyer_num')\n                if reply_elem:\n                    reply_count = reply_elem.inner_text().strip()\n            except:\n                pass\n            \n            try:\n                read_elem = pg.query_selector('.l_posts_num .looknums')\n                if read_elem:\n                    read_count = read_elem.inner_text().strip()\n            except:\n                pass\n            \n            # 获取楼主内容\n            try:\n                content_elem = pg.query_selector('.p_content .d_post_content')\n                content = content_elem.inner_text() if content_elem else \"\"\n            except:\n                content = \"\"\n            \n            results.append({\n                'title': post['title'],\n                'url': full_url,\n                'replies': reply_count,\n                'views': read_count,\n                'content': content[:300] if content else \"\"\n            })\n            print(f\"{i+1}. {post['title'][:40]} | 回复:{reply_count} | 阅读:{read_count}\")\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"Error: {e}\")\n    \n    b.close()\n\nprint(\"\\n=== 分析完成 ===\")\nprint(json.dumps(results[:5], ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\nEOF","timeout":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":90581,"output":787,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239356804,"responseId":"019d901cf9e3861fb446a822cc2f780f"}}
