{"type":"message","id":"34dd6bd8","parentId":"733042a9","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:51:26.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The page content isn't loading properly. The issue might be that the page requires JavaScript rendering. Let me try a different approach - use the `content()` method to get the raw HTML and parse it manually.\n\nActually, looking at the screenshots from before, the page DID load and show posts. The issue is with how I'm trying to parse it. Let me go back to what worked before - the screenshots showed the post list clearly. Let me try taking a screenshot of the full page and also try using different selectors.\n\nLet me try using jQuery-like selectors or just get the full page content with `content()` method.","thinkingSignature":"945ee32aba80143ed2fa3302c9fefdbf81502896fb325f79f5b36bee6b6d8893"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ikkhs28cwuo2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 20 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    pg = b.contexts[0].pages[-1]\n    pg.goto('https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=环世界', wait_until='domcontentloaded', timeout=15000)\n    pg.wait_for_timeout(8000)\n    \n    # 截图看实际内容\n    pg.screenshot(path='/tmp/tieba_list.png', full_page=True)\n    \n    # 尝试用JS获取帖子列表\n    thread_data = pg.evaluate('''\n        () => {\n            const threads = document.querySelectorAll(\"li.j_thread_list\");\n            return Array.from(threads).slice(0, 15).map(t => ({\n                title: t.querySelector(\".threadlist_title a\")?.innerText || \"\",\n                href: t.querySelector(\".threadlist_title a\")?.href || \"\",\n                replyNum: t.querySelector(\".threadlist_reply_num .red\")?.innerText || \"0\",\n                author: t.querySelector(\".threadlist_name .frs-author-name\")?.innerText || \"\"\n            }));\n        }\n    ''')\n    \n    print(f\"Found {len(thread_data)} threads\")\n    for i, t in enumerate(thread_data):\n        if t['title']:\n            print(f\"{i+1}. [{t['replyNum']}回复] {t['title'][:50]}\")\n            print(f\"   作者: {t['author']}\")\n    \n    b.close()\nEOF","timeout":25}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":59731,"output":531,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80342,"cost":{"input":0.0179193,"output":0.0006372,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0197613}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239470308,"responseId":"062e766e199240b6042e2fdce443edff"}}
