{"type":"message","id":"7529b101","parentId":"f3f8e995","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:53:02.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The page loaded but shows the login prompt again. It seems like the Edge browser might have been closed or the page timed out. Let me check the connection status.\n\nWait, looking at the screenshot, it shows \"展开更多\" (show more) at the bottom and some navigation elements, but I can't see the actual post list clearly. Let me try getting the post list with a different approach.\n\nActually, the issue is that the browser might have been left at a login state. Let me reconnect and get the post list.","thinkingSignature":"758908bbb6f9b8ae1ae13da61650ecefda9769cdbf99fa4f7c1a6f004fed3ea2"},{"type":"text","text":"页面加载了但显示用户提示。重新检查连接：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xfeeqjxduotl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 12 python3 -c \"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=8000)\n    pages = b.contexts[0].pages\n    print(f'Pages: {len(pages)}')\n    for pg in pages:\n        print(f'URL: {pg.url[:80]}')\n    b.close()\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62059,"output":283,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82422,"cost":{"input":0.018617699999999997,"output":0.00033959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020162099999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239572773,"responseId":"062e76d4ef8b708899cc340827fe7d25"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c7588e0","parentId":"7529b101","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:53:02.864Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xfeeqjxduotl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pages: 2\nURL: https://tieba.baidu.com/\nURL: https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%E7%8E%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":758,"aggregated":"Pages: 2\nURL: https://tieba.baidu.com/\nURL: https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%E7%8E%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776239582854}}
{"type":"message","id":"27f7e573","parentId":"8c7588e0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:53:17.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, there are 2 pages. The second one is the Rimworld forum. Let me use the second page for scraping instead of the last one. The issue might be that the last page is the one that timed out earlier.","thinkingSignature":"d3b1de0261047fef055f137b50e16c2a40762e9237f714fa277ef8881e1a6fca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k7i66hkln241_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 25 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport json, re\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    \n    # 用第二个页面（贴吧页面）\n    pg = b.contexts[0].pages[1]\n    pg.set_default_timeout(10000)\n    \n    # 获取HTML\n    html = pg.content()\n    \n    # 解析帖子\n    # 方式1：通过正则匹配\n    post_matches = re.findall(r'href=\"(/p/\\d+)\"[^>]*title=\"([^\"]+)\"', html)\n    \n    # 方式2：查找所有链接\n    all_links = re.findall(r'<a[^>]+href=\"(/p/\\d+)\"[^>]*>([^<]+)</a>', html)\n    \n    print(f\"Found {len(post_matches)} post matches\")\n    print(f\"Found {len(all_links)} total links\")\n    \n    # 找帖子标题（通常在threadlist相关的元素里）\n    thread_titles = re.findall(r'class=\"[^\"]*title[^\"]*\"[^>]*>([^<]+)', html)\n    thread_links = re.findall(r'<a[^>]+href=\"(/p/\\d+)\"[^>]*class=\"[^\"]*threadlist[^\"]*\"', html)\n    \n    print(f\"\\nThread titles: {len(thread_titles)}\")\n    for t in thread_titles[:10]:\n        if len(t.strip()) > 5:\n            print(f\"  - {t.strip()[:60]}\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\nThread links: {len(thread_links)}\")\n    for link in thread_links[:10]:\n        print(f\"  - /p/{link}\")\n    \n    b.close()\nEOF","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62406,"output":500,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82986,"cost":{"input":0.0187218,"output":0.0006,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0205266}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239582871,"responseId":"062e76deee1afbea182818e247ec48c6"}}
