{"type":"message","id":"7424bdde","parentId":"aa04c022","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:53:54.433Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qqiai4y3aqfp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Total lines: 90\n\nPost-related lines (3):\n  回复于21小时前\n  回复于04-13\n  回复于04-14"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4820,"aggregated":"Total lines: 90\n\nPost-related lines (3):\n  回复于21小时前\n  回复于04-13\n  回复于04-14","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776239634418}}
{"type":"message","id":"a96210b6","parentId":"7424bdde","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:54:13.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only 3 lines with \"回复\" and they don't contain the post titles. This is strange - the page seems to not have the post list rendered properly. \n\nWait - looking at the earlier screenshots, the page DID show posts. But the text extraction shows very little content. This might mean the content is in images/canvas rather than text, or it's loaded via JavaScript in a way that doesn't expose the text content to Playwright.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use the forum's API directly instead of scraping the page. Baidu Tieba has an API I can use.Or let me try getting the full HTML content and see what's there.","thinkingSignature":"f87fd48057663a436148444ae7ad0243b2fad5b6a0a106a591c94f288f5fd459"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sqquo1crtisi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 20 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    pg = b.contexts[0].pages[1]\n    pg.set_default_timeout(10000)\n    \n    # 用JS获取所有文本内容\n    all_text = pg.evaluate('''() => {\n        // 获取所有元素\n        const elements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n        const texts = [];\n        elements.forEach(el => {\n            if (el.children.length === 0 && el.innerText.trim()) {\n                texts.push({\n                    tag: el.tagName,\n                    class: el.className.substring(0,30),\n                    text: el.innerText.trim().substring(0, 100)\n                });\n            }\n        });\n        return texts.filter(t => t.text.length > 5 && t.text.length < 200);\n    }''')\n    \n    print(f\"Found {len(all_text)} text elements\")\n    \n    # 找帖子标题\n    for item in all_text:\n        text = item['text']\n        if ('吧' not in text and '百度' not in text and '登录' not in text and \n            len(text) > 8 and text.count('\\n') < 3):\n            print(f\"[{item['class']}] {text[:80]}\")\n    \n    b.close()\nEOF","timeout":25}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64303,"output":502,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84885,"cost":{"input":0.0192909,"output":0.0006024,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021098099999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239634439,"responseId":"062e77114967c508bc3b87905ce64c90"}}
