{"type":"message","id":"057e1bfe","parentId":"12376281","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:55:50.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The posts are showing 0 replies and 0 views, and the content is not being extracted. The issue is likely that the page navigation isn't working properly in the CDP session - each `goto` might be opening a new page instead of navigating the current one.\n\nAlso the thread list was found but the actual post titles and content aren't being retrieved correctly. Let me try a different approach - use the forum's tab (最新) to get the latest posts, and try navigating with page clicks instead of goto.\n\nActually, looking at the earlier successful attempts, the issue is that when I use `goto`, it opens in a new page context, not the existing tab. Let me check if there are multiple pages and manage them better.\n\nLet me try creating a new page for each post instead of reusing the same page.","thinkingSignature":"b808e6e4ae614e07bacbbef6066691b86ff5b959919f05fce37128bab35197d9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ujua2nx4vq3x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 45 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport json\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    \n    # 创建新页面来访问帖子\n    page = b.contexts[0].new_page()\n    page.set_default_timeout(8000)\n    \n    results = []\n    # 帖子URL列表\n    post_urls = [\n        ('https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10628392935', '全新Boss单位 白色惊惧MOD 上线创意工坊'),\n        ('https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10621623679', '【MOD更新公告】天工铸造 26/4/4'),\n        ('https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10625960310', '我靠萌螈僵尸真强啊'),\n    ]\n    \n    for i, (url, title) in enumerate(post_urls):\n        try:\n            page.goto(url, wait_until='domcontentloaded', timeout=8000)\n            page.wait_for_timeout(3000)\n            \n            # 获取数据\n            reply_num = page.query_selector('.l_posts_num .replyer_num').inner_text() if page.query_selector('.l_posts_num .replyer_num') else \"0\"\n            view_num = page.query_selector('.l_posts_num .looknums').inner_text() if page.query_selector('.l_posts_num .looknums') else \"0\"\n            \n            # 获取回复内容\n            floors = page.query_selector_all('.l_post')\n            replies = []\n            for floor in floors[:5]:\n                try:\n                    author = floor.query_selector('.p_author .d_name').inner_text() if floor.query_selector('.p_author .d_name') else \"未知\"\n                    content = floor.query_selector('.p_content').inner_text().replace('\\n', ' ')[:150] if floor.query_selector('.p_content') else \"\"\n                    replies.append(f\"{author}: {content}\")\n                except:\n                    pass\n            \n            results.append({\n                'title': title,\n                'url': url,\n                'replies': reply_num,\n                'views': view_num,\n                'floor1_replies': replies\n            })\n            \n            print(f\"{i+1}. 【{reply_num}回复|{view_num}阅读】{title[:40]}\")\n            for r in replies[:3]:\n                print(f\"   {r[:80]}\")\n            print()\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"Error: {e}\")\n    \n    page.close()\n    b.close()\n    \n    # 保存结果\n    with open('/tmp/rimworld_analysis.json', 'w') as f:\n        json.dump(results, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(\"Results saved to /tmp/rimworld_analysis.json\")\nEOF","timeout":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67290,"output":826,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88196,"cost":{"input":0.020187,"output":0.0009912,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022383}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239730706,"responseId":"062e7772ec1e1f83f5b2f4bf01