{"type":"message","id":"90ede6de","parentId":"54f67c47","timestamp":"2026-04-15T07:56:40.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the actual post content. The post is:\n- Title: 全新Boss单位 白色惊惧MOD 上线创意工坊\n- Author: 乃奈奈亚子哦 (修士)\n- Time: 04-10 广东\n- Content: 添加一个全新的boss单位开局会加入殖民地，第一次死亡后会进入敌对状态，击倒之后就可以正常使用技能。强度适中，原版可打，无开发者防护和无定型boss（大面包）有轻度联动\n\n- Replies: 34\n- Views: 102\n\nAnd there are replies from other users discussing the MOD.\n\nNow I can see the data is loading correctly when I use `inner_text('body')`. The issue was that the selectors for reply count weren't matching. Let me now do a proper batch retrieval of multiple posts and analyze them.","thinkingSignature":"991b586d5e4d2bf36dc0d01fbc407edc4c0c03a15e88f217b3405588820e8ce1"},{"type":"text","text":"有数据了！刚才 selector 有问题。重新批量获取：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3bd09ekuiohj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 60 python3 << 'EOF'\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\nimport json\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    b = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp('ws://172.23.96.1:19222/devtools/browser/66e81b27-118a-4faf-a80a-a902a223eec3', timeout=10000)\n    page = b.contexts[0].new_page()\n    page.set_default_timeout(10000)\n    \n    # 帖子URL列表\n    posts = [\n        'https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10628392935',\n        'https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10621623679', \n        'https://tieba.baidu.com/p/10625960310',\n    ]\n    \n    results = []\n    for url in posts:\n        try:\n            page.goto(url, wait_until='domcontentloaded', timeout=10000)\n            page.wait_for_timeout(4000)\n            \n            # 用inner_text提取所有内容\n            content = page.inner_text('body')\n            \n            # 解析关键信息\n            lines = content.split('\\n')\n            \n            # 找标题（在帖子内容前几行）\n            title = \"\"\n            author = \"\"\n            post_time = \"\"\n            reply_count = 0\n            view_count = 0\n            post_content = \"\"\n            \n            # 简单解析\n            content_lines = []\n            capture_content = False\n            for line in lines:\n                if '回复于' in line:\n                    continue\n                if len(line.strip()) > 3:\n                    content_lines.append(line.strip())\n            \n            # 提取楼主的帖子内容（通常在作者名之后）\n            results.append({\n                'url': url,\n                'content_preview': content[:2000]\n            })\n            \n            print(f\"OK: {url}\")\n            print(f\"   Preview: {content[:200]}...\")\n            print()\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"Error: {e}\")\n    \n    page.close()\n    b.close()\n    \n    with open('/tmp/posts_raw.json', 'w') as f:\n        json.dump(results, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\nEOF","timeout":65}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69723,"output":678,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90481,"cost":{"input":0.0209169,"output":0.0008135999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0229353}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776239782193,"responseId":"062e77a6011b4c2fe4cebada42b3e696"}}
